items.title: PARADONTAX PASTE CLASSIC
items.alt: Image with a box of toothpaste
items.description:
Parodontax Fluoride toothpaste helps stop bleeding gums.
  • It also contains fluoride that prevents caries, so you can safely use it every day.
  • Ingredients parodontax toothpaste consists of 70% medicinal active ingredients.
  • It contains mineral salts and plant extracts that give it a unique taste.
  • After 14 days of using parodontax toothpaste, most people liked its unique taste.


HOW TO USE: Brush your teeth two and no more than three times a day, reduce swallowing the paste to a minimum and spit it out.

PACKAGING: 75 ml

items.title: ORAL-B ESSENTIAL DENTAL FLOSS
items.alt: Image with a packaged dental floss product
items.description:
• mint flavored dental floss
  • double-layer thread: strong and pleasant to handle
  • silky texture
  • glides easily, gentle on fingers and gums
  • leaves a feeling of cleanliness and freshness in the mouth
Complete your oral hygiene with dental floss. Oral-B Essential Mint dental floss slides easily between the teeth so you can clean even the most difficult places. The thread is strong and easy to handle. It is gentle on both fingers and gums, and leaves a fresh mint taste and a feeling of cleanliness in the mouth.

items.alt: Image of a cosmetic spray tube and packaging

items.title: ORTHOMOL IMMUN A30 BAGS
items.alt: Image with a blue box of medicine
items.description:
Orthomol Immun is a dietary product for special medical use (balanced diet).

  • It contains micronutrients in a complex composition and with a well-balanced, scientifically based dosage.
  • Orthomol Immun is used for the treatment of nutritionally conditioned immune deficits, related to diet, which you may encounter, for example, after chemotherapy and radiation.
  • Orthomol Immun is intended for people with a weakened immune system, for example after chemotherapy and radiation, in elderly people, in cases of acute and chronic infections and diseases, after surgery.

items.title: ORTHOMOL VISION A30 120 CPS
items.alt: Image with a blue box of medicine
items.description:
Orthomol® Vision is a dietary supplement, important micronutrients for the eyes.

  • With vitamin A, vitamin B2 (riboflavin), zinc, omega and omega-3 fatty acids (DHA) to maintain normal vision.
  • With lutein and zeaxanthin.
  • Orthomol® Vision does not contain gluten or lactose
  • The recommended dose should not be exceeded.
  • A dietary supplement is not a substitute for a varied, balanced diet and a healthy lifestyle.
